{
  "video_id": "rsuB-6-n-MM",
  "title": "Justin Hall-Tipping: Freeing energy from the grid",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we solve these problems?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "We know what they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "Something always seems to stop us."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "I remember March the 15th, 2000."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "The B15 iceberg broke off the Ross Ice Shelf."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "In the newspaper it said"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "\"it was all part of a normal process.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "A little bit further on in the article"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "it said \"a loss that would normally take"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "the ice shelf 50-100 years to replace.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "That same word, \"normal,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "had two different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "almost opposite meanings."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "If we walk into the B15 iceberg"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "when we leave here today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to bump into something"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "a thousand feet tall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "76 miles long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "17 miles wide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to weigh two gigatons."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sorry, there&#39;s nothing normal about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "And yet I think it&#39;s this perspective of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "as humans to look at our world"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "through the lens of normal"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "is one of the forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "that stops us developing real solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "Only 90 days after this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "arguably the greatest discovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "of the last century occurred."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "It was the sequencing for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "of the human genome."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "This is the code that&#39;s in every single one"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "of our 50 trillion cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "that makes us who we are and what we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "And if we just take one cell&#39;s worth"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "of this code and unwind it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a meter long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "two nanometers thick."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "Two nanometers is 20 atoms in thickness."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "And I wondered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "what if the answer to some of our biggest problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "could be found in the smallest of places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "where the difference between what is"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "valuable and what is worthless"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "is merely the addition or subtraction"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "of a few atoms?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "And what"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "if we could get exquisite control"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "over the essence of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "the electron?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "So I started to go around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "finding the best and brightest scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "I could at universities"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "whose collective discoveries have the chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "to take us there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "and we formed a company to build"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "on their extraordinary ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "Six and a half years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "a hundred and eighty researchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "they have some amazing developments"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "in the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "and I will show you three of those today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "such that we can stop burning up our planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "and instead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "we can generate all the energy we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "right where we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "cleanly, safely, and cheaply."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "Think of the space that we spend"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "most of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "A tremendous amount of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "is coming at us from the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "We like the light that comes into the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "but in the middle of summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "all that heat is coming into the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re trying to keep cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "In winter, exactly the opposite is happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re trying to heat up"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "the space that we&#39;re in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "and all that is trying to get out through the window."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "Wouldn&#39;t it be really great"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "if the window could flick back the heat"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "into the room if we needed it"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "or flick it away before it came in?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "One of the materials that can do this"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "is a remarkable material, carbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "that has changed its form in this incredibly beautiful reaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "where graphite is blasted by a vapor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "and when the vaporized carbon condenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "it condenses back into a different form:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "chickenwire rolled up."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "But this chickenwire carbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "called a carbon nanotube,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "is a hundred thousand times smaller"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "than the width of one of your hairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a thousand times"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "more conductive than copper."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "How is that possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "One of the things about working at the nanoscale"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "is things look and act very differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "You think of carbon as black."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "Carbon at the nanoscale"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "is actually transparent"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "and flexible."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "And when it&#39;s in this form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "if I combine it with a polymer"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "and affix it to your window"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "when it&#39;s in its colored state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "it will reflect away all heat and light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "and when it&#39;s in its bleached state"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "it will let all the light and heat through"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "and any combination in between."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "To change its state, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "takes two volts from a millisecond pulse."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "And once you&#39;ve changed its state, it stays there"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "until you change its state again."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "As we were working on this incredible"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "discovery at University of Florida,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "we were told to go down the corridor"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "to visit another scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "and he was working"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "on a pretty incredible thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "Imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "if we didn&#39;t have to rely"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "on artificial lighting to get around at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d have to see at night, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "This lets you do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a nanomaterial, two nanomaterials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "a detector and an imager."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "The total width of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "is 600 times smaller"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "than the width of a decimal place."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "And it takes all the infrared available at night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "converts it into an electron"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "in the space of two small films,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "and is enabling you to play an image"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "which you can see through."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to show to TEDsters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "the first time, this operating."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "Firstly I&#39;m going to show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "the transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "Transparency is key."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a film that you can look through."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "And then I&#39;m going to turn the lights out."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "And you can see, off a tiny film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "incredible clarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "As we were working on this, it dawned on us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "this is taking infrared radiation, wavelengths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "and converting it into electrons."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "What if we combined it"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "with this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "Suddenly you&#39;ve converted energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "into an electron on a plastic surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "that you can stick on your window."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "But because it&#39;s flexible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "it can be on any surface whatsoever."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "The power plant of tomorrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "is no power plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "We talked about generating and using."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "We want to talk about storing energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "the best thing we&#39;ve got going"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "is something that was developed in France"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "a hundred and fifty years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "the lead acid battery."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 497260.0,
      "text": "In terms of dollars per what&#39;s stored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 497260.0,
      "end_time": 499260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s simply the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 499260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "Knowing that we&#39;re not going to put fifty of"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "these in our basements to store our power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "we went to a group at University of Texas at Dallas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "and we gave them this diagram."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "It was in actually a diner"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "outside of Dallas/Fort Worth Airport."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "We said, \"Could you build this?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "And these scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "instead of laughing at us, said, \"Yeah.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "And what they built was eBox."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "EBox is testing new nanomaterials"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "to park an electron on the outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 528260.0,
      "text": "hold it until you need it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 528260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "and then be able to release it and pass it off."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "Being able to do that means"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 535260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "that I can generate energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "cleanly, efficiently and cheaply"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "right where I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "And if I don&#39;t need it, I can convert it"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "back up on the window"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 552260.0,
      "text": "to energy, light, and beam it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "line of site, to your place."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "And for that I do not need"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 558260.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "an electric grid between us."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "The grid of tomorrow is no grid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 569260.0,
      "text": "and energy, clean efficient energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 569260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "will one day be free."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 576260.0,
      "end_time": 580260.0,
      "text": "If you do this, you get the last puzzle piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 580260.0,
      "end_time": 583260.0,
      "text": "which is water."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "Each of us, every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 596260.0,
      "text": "need just eight glasses of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 596260.0,
      "end_time": 599260.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re human."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 599260.0,
      "end_time": 601260.0,
      "text": "When we run out of water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 601260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "as we are in some parts of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 605260.0,
      "text": "and soon to be in other parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to have to get this from the sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 611260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s going to require us to build desalination plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 611260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "19 trillion dollars is what we&#39;re going to have to spend."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 616260.0,
      "text": "These also require tremendous amounts of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 618260.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s going to require twice the world&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "supply of oil to run the pumps"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 620260.0,
      "end_time": 623260.0,
      "text": "to generate the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re simply not going to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 627260.0,
      "text": "But in a world where energy is freed"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 627260.0,
      "end_time": 629260.0,
      "text": "and transmittable"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 629260.0,
      "end_time": 631260.0,
      "text": "easily and cheaply, we can take any water"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 631260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "wherever we are"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 637260.0,
      "text": "and turn it into whatever we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 637260.0,
      "end_time": 639260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m glad to be working with"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 639260.0,
      "end_time": 641260.0,
      "text": "incredibly brilliant and kind scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 641260.0,
      "end_time": 643260.0,
      "text": "no kinder than"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 643260.0,
      "end_time": 645260.0,
      "text": "many of the people in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 645260.0,
      "end_time": 648260.0,
      "text": "but they have a magic look at the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 648260.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m glad to see their discoveries"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 653260.0,
      "text": "coming out of the lab and into the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 653260.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been a long time in coming for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "18 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 664260.0,
      "text": "I saw a photograph in the paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 664260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "It was taken by Kevin Carter"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "who went to the Sudan"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "to document their famine there."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 672260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve carried this photograph with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 672260.0,
      "end_time": 674260.0,
      "text": "every day since then."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 677260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a picture of a little girl dying of thirst."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 687260.0,
      "end_time": 692260.0,
      "text": "By any standard this is wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 695260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 698260.0,
      "end_time": 701260.0,
      "text": "We can do better than this."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 701260.0,
      "end_time": 704260.0,
      "text": "We should do better than this."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 704260.0,
      "end_time": 706260.0,
      "text": "And whenever I go round"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 706260.0,
      "end_time": 708260.0,
      "text": "to somebody who says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "\"You know what, you&#39;re working on something that&#39;s too difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;ll never happen. You don&#39;t have enough money."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have enough time."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 719260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s something much more interesting around the corner,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 719260.0,
      "end_time": 721260.0,
      "text": "I say, \"Try saying that to her.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 721260.0,
      "end_time": 723260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I say in my mind. And I just say"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 723260.0,
      "end_time": 726260.0,
      "text": "\"thank you,\" and I go on to the next one."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 726260.0,
      "end_time": 729260.0,
      "text": "This is why we have to solve our problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 729260.0,
      "end_time": 734260.0,
      "text": "and I know the answer as to how"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 734260.0,
      "end_time": 738260.0,
      "text": "is to be able to get exquisite control"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 738260.0,
      "end_time": 741260.0,
      "text": "over a building block of nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 741260.0,
      "end_time": 743260.0,
      "text": "the stuff of life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 743260.0,
      "end_time": 745260.0,
      "text": "the simple electron."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 745260.0,
      "end_time": 747260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 747260.0,
      "end_time": 759260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}